subject: Swimming
Deaths (Obituaries)
lead_paragraph: Moriarty succeeded a legend, Bob Kiphuth, at Yale and then built his own legend, training gold medal swimmers like Don Schollander and coaching the United States divers in the 1960 Olympics.
